name: Jvee Veneracion
text: You guys still watching STD? It's a mess. Everytime Michael Spock does a whispered dialogue, I just roll my eyes.

replies.text: Eh, it's fine, as long as you don't expect it to have the same tone as TNG, DS9, etc. (We have Orville for that.) Also, calling it STD probably doesnt have. The second season seems better than the first.
hmmm ok pa din sa akin so far.
